  "abstract": "The Board is adopting, and inviting comment on, an interim final rule to amend its regulations for processing requests under the Freedom of Information Act (\"FOIA\") pursuant to the FOIA Improvement Act of 2016 (the \"Act\"). The amendments clarify and update procedures for requesting information from the Board, extend the deadline for administrative appeals, and add information on dispute resolution services.",
